00:24:03,740 --> 00:24:08,500
Oops! It looks like I've arrived at the wrong time.

323
00:24:08,500 --> 00:24:11,150
Sensei, please stop acting so blatant in trying to fill time.

324
00:24:11,150 --> 00:24:15,950
I already told you this isn't a cigarette. It's a lollipop.

325
00:24:15,950 --> 00:24:17,520
Don't try to laugh it off!

326
00:24:18,090 --> 00:24:22,450
It's smoking because I’m licking it so fast.

